Patch Set 7: Code-Review-1

Please set up an "extras" entry for swift instead of just moving the dependency to test-requirements.txt. That will signal to users that you know what dependencies there are for the backend, but that they are optional, and still allow someone to do the equivalent of "pip install glance[swift]" to get those dependencies. Nova and oslo.versionedobjects have examples in their setup.cfg if you need a template.
